Pacific Map, summer 1941

Eric Rauchway

6/10/2022

Map data draws principally from Natural Earth datasets, at various resolutions. Ive drawn for reference on other sources, including Andr Ouredniks historical basemaps repository; for occupied China, I relied on Greg Huff, World War II and Southeast Asia. For colors I drew mainly from CARTOcolors. When all else has failed Ive looked up latitudes and longitudes in Wikipedia.
